{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A shooting adventure RPG game, where you play as a gunslinger in Westland. You can explore the area, encounter fights with Outlaws and wild beasts , accept quest and side mission, unlock items and equipment.    In the main story, your character will play an important role in stopping an evil outlaw syndicate that terrorized the Westland. And to achieve that you will unveil the legends of this mystery land!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot0_2.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/mystery.jpg?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will battle with different type of enemies. From Outlaws to Wild Beasts. Different weapon options are available to choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/Screenshot_2025-01-01_132728.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot1.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Aside from the story and battle system, there will Quest system where player can accept quest from Tavern. And also player can buy items and equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot7_2.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot3.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/bounty.jpg?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are also side activities where player can try to complete and unlock. Such as Horse Racing and Fishing system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot4.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot5.png?t=1739701845\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739701845","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/page.bg.jpg?t=1739701845","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/ba32fa4401e93f77ee57f1b1eace5fd205f0846b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739701845","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/ba32fa4401e93f77ee57f1b1eace5fd205f0846b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739701845","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3449150,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A shooting adventure RPG game, where you play as a gunslinger in Westland. You can explore the area, encounter fights with Outlaws and wild beasts , accept quest and side mission, unlock items and equipment.    In the main story, your character will play an important role in stopping an evil outlaw syndicate that terrorized the Westland. And to achieve that you will unveil the legends of this mystery land!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242510/extras/screenshot0_2.png?t=1739701845\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img cl